title: Beethoven - Violin Concerto - Karajan, BPO - Ferras, Mutter
description:
Beethoven: Violin Concerto. [two versions]

 - That last violin concerto upload seemed to be popular, so here's a similar one.

Karajan (also) recorded the Beethoven Violin Concerto twice for DG with the BPO. The first time was in 1967 with Christian Ferras, and the second was in 1979 with Anne-Sophie Mutter. Here are both versions. Again, you decide which you prefer.

Please enjoy.
